## du sagst

### Metadata

```yaml
title: du sagst
type: application/vnd.google-apps.document
created: 2019-08-30T20:43:50.205Z
modified: 2019-08-30T20:50:07.207Z
path: /My Drive/My Texts / Presentations/#PUBLISHED_DONE/du sagst
