﻿The Waltz into the Future: How Austria Innovates Music


Austria is considered by many the home of music. Think Mozart, the "Sound of Music", Herbert von Karajan, the New Year's Concert and the Viennese Waltz. But time does not stand still. This panel explores how Austrian musicians, institutions and startups are trailblazing the future of (classical) music and redefining the business of creativity.




